thread.title: Susan McTaggart
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Susan McTaggart

author: Susan McTaggart
title: Susan McTaggart
text: The product is great. The only problem is the courier - he called me even though I was home and left promptly because I was on the phone. Not sure what happened there. Then I had to go to some obscure place to pick up my order. Otherwise, everything is really good. I have ordered before with absolutely no issues - hence my five star rating.
